g you the best deals and gifts. As a result, shipping may take a little longer than usual. We thank you in advance for your understanding and assure you that your patience will be rewarded with an exceptional skincare experience!</p></div></div></article></div></div><div data-accordion="" style="padding-bottom: "><div data-control="" data-index="4" data-key="content" class="chevron iCon-right text- item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1732193988646" class="element-wrap" data-icon="eicon-animation-text" data-id="1732193988646"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-exc=""><p><strong>Why is delivery taking longer than usual?</strong></p></div></div><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:var(--gf_gs-color2-brand)"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:var(--gf_gs-color5-accent)"></span></button></div><div data-content="" style="margin-top: ; background-color: none"><article data-index="4" data-key="content1" class="item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1732193988790" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1732193988790"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Deliveries may also take longer than expected during this period due to high volume of packages received by the courier. Keep an eye on your tracking link for updates and estimated delivery time.</p></div></div></article></div></div><div data-accordion="" style="padding-bottom: "><div data-control="" data-index="5" data-key="content" class="chevron iCon-right text- item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1732193988761" class="element-wrap" data-icon="eicon-animation-text" data-id="1732193988761"><div cla